Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.320
As a marketer, you want to understand to which marketing actions

00:00:04.320 --> 00:00:08.460
or advertising campaigns have the most impact on your goals.

00:00:08.460 --> 00:00:14.850
How each campaign contributed to acquiring users and the path that led them to convert.

00:00:14.849 --> 00:00:19.439
One of the most important questions you want to be able to answer is,

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:23.609
what marketing action to attribute a sale or conversion to.

00:00:23.609 --> 00:00:27.119
Attribution reports will help you answer this question.

00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:29.310
In this lesson, we will learn about

00:00:29.309 --> 00:00:34.519
the different attribution models and how to use them in Google Analytics.

